
This directory contains a few files that sphinx2 can use for
a task.

  demo.corpus   is the original corpus as given to the lmtool web page.
                see the main website for more info at
                   
                     http://www.speech.cs.cmu.edu/sphinx/

  demo.dic      the pronunciation dictionary for the task

  demo.handdict where you add your own pronuciations (a hand-made
                dictionary)

  demo.lm       the actual ARPABO language model for the task

  demo.sent     the sentences as they were actually processed

  demo.sent.arpabo arpabo models of the sentences

  demo.token    token counts for each 'word'

  demo.vocab    the vocabulary of the task

  demo_10000.map   the state map for each HMM needed in the task

  demo_10000.phone the triphone map for the task


Not all of these are needed, but they're all here.
